Subject: [PATCH 5.12 107/178] radeon: use memcpy_to/fromio for UVD fw upload
Date:   Mon, 21 Jun 2021 18:15:21 +0200
Message-Id: <20210621154926.410094969@linuxfoundation.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.32.0
